# SECURITY: never commit DB backups — they contain bcrypt passwordHash / pinHash
# of real users. Previously only specific filename prefixes were ignored; the
# daily backup commits (e.g. backups/2026-07-06.json) leaked hashes to the
# public repo. Block the whole directory; if a future script needs to commit a
# non-sensitive file under backups/, add an explicit !exception line.
backups/*.json
backups/*.jsonl
backups/*.db
backups/*.sqlite
